  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to neon</title>

    <para>The <application>neon</application> package is an HTTP and WebDAV
    client library, with a C interface.</para>

    &lfs71_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
